page.text: A full set of products for print and web, creating the corporate identity and branding of the Real Estate company Park & Villas. Using different graphic programs I created a variety of useful products, such as brochures, adds for web and print, videos, roll-ups, invitations and datasheets etc. The brand of Park & Villas should transmit green and environmental friendly concept offering high quality and lifestyle homes. All their projects are located in smaller cities in Sweden.
